title: 1926–27 Swiss National Ice Hockey Championship
text:
The 1926–27 <a href="List%20of%20Swiss%20ice%20hockey%20champions">Swiss National Ice Hockey Championship</a> was the 17th edition of the national ice hockey championship in <a href="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>. <a href="HC%20Davos">HC Davos</a> won the championship by defeating <a href="HC%20Rosey%20Gstaad">HC Rosey Gstaad</a> in the final.
First round.
Eastern Series.
<a href="HC%20Davos">HC Davos</a> qualified for the final.
Western Series.
Final.
<a href="HC%20Rosey%20Gstaad">HC Rosey Gstaad</a> qualified for the final.
